</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,1194,1687,1714]" pageId="18" pageNumber="500" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,1364,2038]" box="[199,1194,1687,1714]" pageId="18" pageNumber="500">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1687,1713]" pageId="18" pageNumber="500">Distribution.</emphasis>
Only known from the 
<typeStatus box="[608,656,1688,1714]" pageId="18" pageNumber="500">type</typeStatus>
locality, situated in north-eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1037,1082,1688,1714]" name="Iran" pageId="18" pageNumber="500">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[1098,1181,1688,1714]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="14.[151,250,1739,1763]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1073,1715]" captionTargetId="figure-52@14.[151,1435,1073,1715]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 12. Distribution of A. eremicum, A. flavissimum sp. nov., A. occidentale sp. nov., and A. preoccipitale sp. nov." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5531659" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5531659/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="500">Fig. 12</figureCitation>
